# The /api/demo route (live "try with your own prompt" agent) routes through
# Vercel AI Gateway: streamText({ model: "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6", ... }).
#
# On a Vercel deployment that has gateway access (most teams do by default),
# nothing needs to be set — auth is auto-injected. For local dev, run
# `vercel link` once and `vercel env pull .env.local` to grab the gateway
# credentials, or set AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY manually.
#
# AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=
